modules.description: This module defines a function `catt_tm` that takes a string and a list of strings, performing an operation to export or process terms in a structured format. It works with basic string data types, organizing them into a list structure for batch handling. A concrete use case includes exporting parsed terms to external files or intermediate representations for further processing.

This module includes a function `catt_tm` that processes a string and a list of strings, organizing them into a structured format for batch term handling. It operates primarily on string and list data types, with a concrete use case involving the export of parsed terms to external files or intermediate representations. The module supports structured term manipulation without integrating with other modules.
